{"type": "article", "id": 13157, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-07T08:00:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11731, "name": "水杯"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 32, "name": "时尚"}, {"id": 7612, "name": "Disney"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104233cNzPIGn8V367MWae.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tWooden Aquarelle by Meike Harde<br>\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t来自德国的设计师 Meike Harde 通过给木材表面上色，制成了五彩缤纷的木板，并打造了一系列浪漫的家具，包括屏风，边桌，茶几等。她的方法是把各色颜料倒在木材表面，让它们自由蔓延，交融，等颜料完全干后，在木材表面刷一层透明漆，最终做成这些五颜六色的木板，由此也启发人们自由给木材上色，让家具变得更加缤纷有趣。这是<a href=\"http://meikeharde.com/\" target=\"_blank\">她的个人主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143546cA3ZFCy8g7OLN6T4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143546t7YWuv0lGJKZck9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143547LZV04SYXy1bEDsdf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143547JplhUAQmPa3zGZD6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74270833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143548xlDarXoswvMiSO03.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143548hb8sZy0crojPUk7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143549jaIRZKroqHnsBG9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143549103Mgaz28nKZ7sjk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143550ACdcv7Su3ZDsqt1Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143550J5iMXeufwhvq24Wp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143551u5myNMf6gRJTYPsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143551pdu21chk8sYSJjNE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPinnacle+Apple Watch by Nico Gerard\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>有人痴迷智能科技的酷炫，有人执著于传统工艺的优雅，来自硅谷的 Nico Gerard 则干脆把两者做到了一块手表上，这款叫做 “Pinnacle+Apple Watch” 的手表正面是传统瑞士表，背面则安装了一个 38mm 的 Apple Watch 表盘，这下你的手腕正面背面都闲不着了。这款手表目前有银色和金色两种款式可以选择，已经投入生产。不过，我们一直觉得贪心的设计往往容易陷入尴尬，不妨继续观望一下。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140753UXzfAKxt9GIZ3VO1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143552ySxR8jplMvkVNsw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53178484\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143552d81YVafSze2nNqc9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143552BHx1T5AetlyPbOCI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143553fBJgPYW5Uqy7XNG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tStockholm by Vifa\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>丹麦印象品牌 Vifa 近日推出了一套看上去完全不像音箱的音箱。这套看起来异常低调的名叫“斯德哥尔摩”，而和名字一样，这套音箱满满全是北欧风格。音箱采用无线设计，可以自由摆放而免遭繁复的线材的困扰，目前在颜色上有红色、沙黄色、蓝色等不同选择，可以根据家居环境找到自己满意的选择。音箱售价 1499 欧元（约合 10100 元人民币），这是<a href=\"http://www.vifa.dk/shop/stockholm/c-24/p-116\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143553j8vJag7LNIWyocV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143554HDXQo73ANlVdWuZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143554JCdeVfLh3pt4RTmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143555FzJdLq76GuWo4xYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66623037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143555H20pGVuwTUJDPboK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t“Invisible” Bathroom Sink by Victor Vasilev\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>玻璃和大理石的组合总是能够撞击出独特的美感，近日，来自意大利的建筑师 Victor Vasilev 推出了一个“隐形”洗手台。他用三块正方体大理石组成洗手台的主体，在最左侧的大理石上嵌入了玻璃材料洗漱盆，整体看上去美轮美奂。Victor Vasilev 曾在以色列、米兰等不同地区工作和学习，作品有着强烈个人风格，简洁但极具美感，这是<a href=\"http://www.victorvasilev.com/\" target=\"_blank\">他的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看他更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143556hQt5BuyPlJLzTs3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143556dkD0Wm9xTgsPAoKn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071435567EPTm0ujnokqeFZv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143557qM85ZzAHoYrN3GPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tYoung At Heart by Disney &amp; Vans \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Disney 和 Vans 之前发布的 “Young At Heart” 系列近日又出新招，它们在原来的基础上新增加的两款图案，一款是白底色配卡通人物米奇，另一款则是粉色配米妮。更重要的是，它们现在推出了个人定制化的 “Young At Heart” 系列，款式有 Vans SK8-Hi，Slip on 和 Old Skool II 背包等等，<a href=\"http://www.vans.com/customs?cm_mmc=LinkShare-_-Affiliate-_-je6NUbpObpQ-_-335851&amp;utm_source=linkshare&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=je6NUbpObpQ\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以定制属于自己的 “Young At Heart”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143557XL2qdZhcsfG6RDo8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143558CRwbYeq2idE6TcQ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143558K4M2ti0JLOFElNsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tLife Measured Pitcher by MOLD &amp; Visibility \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t视频设计网站 MOLD 和布鲁克林设计工作室内 Visibility 合作推出了一个大的“量杯”，它是一个设计非常简单的玻璃杯，杯壁上被套了不同颜色的硅胶圈，你可以调整硅胶圈的位置来满足不同情形下对于水量的需求，浇花，喝茶，或者单纯的喝水，都是一个简单而实用的工具。不过，是不是看起来蛮像矿泉水瓶套了个橡胶圈。（走开，当然不一样啦！）这是<a href=\"https://thisismold.com/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143559E02GgzA8V7Mebqx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143559UPF0vw6yrhpmdgX2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143600bsVzLWqXQmyN0Dt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143600yPVlbGjI0kf6DO7K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071436010iktZrdJBFN1Hf5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143601chxnE1Hl5JT9tXwP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143601mN4FXztrpdcYIwR3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607143602Lr3FvxKPDs9C4AlQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}